title: cant launch
body: i cant launch the game, i tried uninstalling and reinstalling it still wont work what going on?

replies.body: Well it was more like not being able to launch the game itself, double clicking it would only bring out an error stating that the game isnt currently available but I ended up deleting all my files for league and reinstalled them, it was a long process but it finally worked. Thank you for trying to help I really appreciate it.

I'd like to help you out here, but need some more details of your issue.  When you say you can't launch the game, what are you referring to exactly (patcher, client, a match)?  Are you receiving any errors, or black screens?  Anything could help.  Thanks!

Greetings,
